-- Bundestag President Wants Euro-Area Transaction Tax, Welt Says
-- B y   A l l i s o n   C o n n o l l y
-- 2012-01-20T06:43:29Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-01-20/bundestag-president-wants-euro-area-transaction-tax-welt-says.html
Bundestag President Norbert Lammert
said he wants a financial transaction tax to be introduced in as
many countries as possible, “at least” in the euro area,  Die
Welt  reported .  A transaction tax is “appropriate and overdue,” the
newspaper cited him as saying.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Allison Connolly in  Frankfurt  at 
 aconnolly4@bloomberg.net .  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Phil Serafino at   pserafino@bloomberg.net . 